      Parameters:
      s - The starting color of which to start the interpolation at
      e - The ending color of which to end the interpolation at
      t - The interpolation parameter ([0, 1])
      Returns:
      The interpolated color
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - When a null parameter is provided
